=== unknown currency ===
invalid currency "xyz"; valid: ars, aud, bdt, brl, cad, chf, clp, cny, cop, czk, dkk, egp, eur, gbp, hkd, huf, idr, ils, inr, jpy, kes, krw, mxn, myr, ngn, nok, nzd, pen, php, pkr, pln, ron, rub, sek, sgd, thb, try, uah, usd, vnd, zar
example: recu add --name Netflix --amount 9.99 --currency usd --interval monthly

=== unknown interval ===
invalid interval "hourly"; valid: weekly, monthly, quarterly, yearly
example: recu add --name Netflix --interval monthly --amount 9.99 --currency usd
